1. *Slušaj* me dobro, ovo je veoma važno. (Listen to me carefully, this is very important.)
2. Molim te, *slušaj* svoju majku i nemoj da joj praviš probleme. (Please, listen to your mother and don't cause her any problems.)
3. On *sluša* muziku dok radi, to ga opušta. (He listens to music while he works, it relaxes him.)
4. Da li si *slušao* vesti ujutru? (Did you listen to the news this morning?)
5. Uvek moraš da *slušaš* svoj unutrašnji glas kada donosiš važne odluke. (You always have to listen to your inner voice when making important decisions.)
6. *Slušajte* pažljivo, imam jednu ideju. (Listen carefully, I have an idea.)
7. Deca, *slušajte* šta vam kaže učiteljica. (Children, listen to what your teacher is telling you.)
8. *Slušaću* tvoj savet jer znam da mi uvek daješ dobre ideje. (I will listen to your advice because I know you always give me good ideas.)
9. Ne mogu da verujem da mi nisi *slušao* kada sam ti govorila o tome. (I can't believe you didn't listen to me when I was talking to you about that.)
10. *Slušajmo* jedni druge i pokušajmo da nađemo rešenje zajedno. (Let's listen to each other and try to find a solution together.)